I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 132rb-136va)&#xD;
I-6) Yǝweddǝsǝwwa mälaʿǝkt... “The angels praise Her...” (fols. 136va-138vb)&#xD;
